        {
          "name": "2. Search Venues",
          "id": "822f3146-b930-4568-a15c-15f6a17be67c",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"page\": 1, // optional, number or null, default values on backend is 1\n    \"per_page\": 25, // optional, number or null, default values on backend is 50\n    \"city\": \"\", // optional, string or null, if provided venues will be filtered by city otherwise all venues will return\n    \"state\": \"\", // optional, string or null, if provided venues will be filtered by state otherwise all venues will return\n    \"country\": \"\", // optional, string or null, if provided venues will be filtered by country otherwise all venues will return\n    \"is_active\": true, // optional, boolean or null, default true, if true only active venues will be returned else all active and non-active venues will be returned\n    \"search\": \"\", // optional, string or null, if provided system will search this string by name, address, city, description\n    \"sort_by\": \"\", // optional, string or null, only valide venue columns are allowed, [\"id\", \"address\", \"city\", \"country\", \"created_at\", \"currency\", \"description\", \"email\", \"is_active\", \"latitude\", \"longitude\", \"name\", \"owner_id\", \"phone_number\", \"postal_code\", \"qr_code_url\", \"slug\", \"state\", \"timezone\", \"updated_at\"], default to \"name\"\n    \"sort_direction\": \"\" // optional, string or null, only [\"asc\", \"ASC\", \"desc\", \"DESC\"] values are allowed, default to \"asc\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{api_v0_base_url}}/venues/search",
              "host": [
                "{{api_v0_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "venues",
                "search"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Search venues with optional filters, sorting, and pagination.\n\nMethod & URL\n- GET {{api_v0_base_url}}/venues/search\n\nRequest body fields\n- page: Optional number for the page to return. Backend default is 1.\n- per_page: Optional number for page size. Backend default is 50.\n- city: Optional string to filter venues by city.\n- state: Optional string to filter venues by state.\n- country: Optional string to filter venues by country.\n- is_active: Optional boolean. Defaults to true; when true, only active venues are returned.\n- search: Optional string matched against venue name, address, city, and description.\n- sort_by: Optional string naming the venue column to sort by. Defaults to name.\n- sort_direction: Optional string with asc or desc. Defaults to asc.\n\nFiltering, sorting, and pagination\n- Filters can be combined to narrow results by location, active status, and free-text search.\n- Sorting is applied using sort_by and sort_direction.\n- Pagination is controlled with page and per_page.\n\n200 response\n- Returns success=true and data as an array of venue objects. Venue objects include core venue details such as id, name, address/location fields, status, and operating hours."
          },
          "response": []
        },
